parameters: Did that fool Zack send you here? I'm
keeping this engine, I need it to power my
lighting system. It's dark down here.

hidden somewhere in this cellar. Find it for me,
and I'll give you the engine.

the security system. Here, take the engine.
Obtained Engine! Now Zack can fix the bridge.
Fine take it. Punk ass bitch...

finally hack into the security system and get

part of the backup system mentioned in the terminal.

events.name: Spa Manager Serene
events.note: Wasteland Hot Springs Resort Quest NPC

parameters: Welcome, weary traveler. I am Serene, manager of what will be the Wasteland Hot Springs Resort.
I've discovered natural hot springs here that have healing properties - a miracle in this harsh world!
I want to create a neutral zone where all factions can come to relax, heal, and perhaps find common ground.
Will you help me build this oasis of peace in our violent wasteland?
